 speed distribution but\ndistinguishing between different underlying distributions remains difficult.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jul 2012 13:20:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Nov 2012 10:53:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-11-19"}
