 arms, but it is still\nevolving far from steady state. A particular transient configuration that is a\nqualitative match to HD142527 is seen at 1.7Myr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jul 2012 14:15:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
